  "snippet": "Hi Alex, As promised, here&#39;s the consolidated information you&#39;ll need for the cross-departmental project: Technical Specifications from IT 1. Integration points: • API Gateway endpoints: /",
  "body": "Hi Alex,\n\nAs promised, here’s the consolidated information you’ll need for the cross-departmental project:\n\nTechnical Specifications from IT\n1. Integration points:\n   • API Gateway endpoints: /inventory, /orders, /analytics\n   • Authentication: OAuth 2.0 with JWT tokens issued by our IdP\n   • Data format: JSON (v2 schema attached in Confluence doc #IT-XD-34)\n\n2. Performance metrics:\n   • ≤ 250 ms average response time (p95 ≤ 400 ms)\n   • 99.9 % monthly uptime\n   • Batch data sync window: 02:00–04:00 UTC nightly\n\n3. Security & Compliance:\n   • TLS 1.3 for all in-flight data\n   • AES-256-GCM encryption at rest (GCP KMS-managed keys)\n   • PII fields tokenised before persisting to the shared data lake\n   • Quarterly penetration testing (next window: 5–9 Aug)\n\n4. Upcoming Milestones:\n   • Dev environment ready: 12 May\n   • Integrated QA build: 26 May\n   • UAT sign-off: 13 Jun\n\nLet me know if you need anything else or would like to set up a quick sync.\n\nBest regards,\nJane\n"
}","annotations":null}

